00:41:02,900 --> 00:41:06,070
But they don't like me.

686
00:41:07,710 --> 00:41:09,870
Excuse me, Maurice.

687
00:41:11,210 --> 00:41:13,370
Congratulations, Edna.

688
00:41:13,450 --> 00:41:17,180
Can I buy you a drink?
All right.

689
00:41:20,220 --> 00:41:23,210
Another week and I'd have wiped
the floor with you. Like hell.

690
00:41:32,870 --> 00:41:36,330
You haven't said anything
