or totalitarian type of regime?

693
00:41:46,350 --> 00:41:48,280
Well, I suppose that's true.

694
00:41:48,350 --> 00:41:50,280
It'll make you think.

695
00:41:55,590 --> 00:41:58,350
Ed, are you all right?

696
00:41:58,430 --> 00:42:01,330
