697
00:42:02,600 --> 00:42:06,090
Yeah. I feel-

698
00:42:06,170 --> 00:42:09,600
What?
Well,

699
00:42:14,010 --> 00:42:15,940
manly.

700
00:42:16,010 --> 00:42:18,980
Like a man.

701
00:42:19,050 --> 00:42:23,070
Ruth-Anne, do you realize
I did something today,

702
00:42:23,150 --> 00:42:26,050
well, that I've never done before.

703
00:42:26,120 --> 00:42:30,960
And it was kinda like
the first time I was with Lightfeather.

704
00:42:31,030 --> 00:42:35,090
Well, only that was
just between me and her.

705
00:42:35,160 --> 00:42:39,070
But afterwards I felt,
well, light.

706
00:42:39,130 --> 00:42:43,730
And this, well,
this was between me and Cicely.

707
00:42:44,810 --> 00:42:46,740
But I don't feel light at all.

708
00:42:48,480 --> 00:42:52,170
I feel... bigger.

709
00:42:57,790 --> 00:43:00,620
So, I'd say we did
pretty well tonight.

710
00:43:00,690 --> 00:43:03,250
Yeah?
Yeah.

711
00:43:03,320 --> 00:43:05,790
You all right?
Yeah.

712
00:43:05,860 --> 00:43:08,850
I just always worry about things
when they're over, you know?

713
00:43:08,930 --> 00:43:12,060
Was everything all right?
