714
00:43:12,130 --> 00:43:14,070
I guess it's just a female thing.

715
00:43:14,140 --> 00:43:18,230
Hey, 87% turnout.
No, uh, late precinct returns.

716
00:43:18,310 --> 00:43:21,400
No disputed ballots.

